title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs. Liverpool - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Having lost four of their first five Premier League home games against Liverpool, Brighton are now unbeaten in their last two against the Reds at the Amex Stadium in the competition. title: Everton vs. Southampton - English Premier League 2024/2025

As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

title: Al Ahli (KSA) vs Kawasaki (JPN) - AFC Champions League Elite 2024/25 - Final
description: Al-Ahli will face Kawasaki Frontale for the first time in the AFC Champions League elite and for the first time against a Japanese team. Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament. All previous finals were between Al-Hilal and Urawa Red Diamonds, with Al-Hilal winning one title in 2019 and Urawa winning two titles in 2017 and 2

description: Alvins too short to ride an exhilarating new amusement park ride, so he devises a plan to sneak on afterhours.  On a ski trip, Alvin convinces Theodore theres a Yeti nearby, making life miserable for the rest of the family.

title: Alvinnn!!! And The Chipmunks: Taken / The Flying Beast
description: The boys imaginations run wild when Dave disappears. When they finally find him, theyre convinced hes a zombie.  Alvin tries to convince Dave that hes being hunted by a flying beast.

description: The Ninja Turtles are on the run and...alone. Leonardo is a leader but who is he without anyone to lead? Leo now has to stop Bishop and her Mechazoids while trying to save his brothers.

title: Tales of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mikey Does The Right Thing
description: To save his brothers, Mikey needs the help of Bishops intern, ROD. But Rod wants something in return... to be turned into a MUTANT! To save the day, Mikey has to become... RESPONSIBLE.

title: The Twisted Timeline of Sammy and Raj: Sofa So Good / So Much Drama

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Operation: Swap-Anzee / Snowmageddon
description: The Space Agency sends Private to the moon. His ticket is downgraded to one-way and the other birds cant monkey around if they hope to get him home again.  Snowmageddon hits and traps Skipper and Marlene in the convenience store with X.

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Tunnel Of Love / Skipper Makes Perfect
description: When a sneeze from Rico causes the underground tunnel system beneath the zoo to rupture Skipper calls in 4 beavers to fix the situation.  Skippers having one of those perfect days, and he decides to use the opportunity to settle an old score.

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: The Penguin Who Loved Me
description: When Doris the Dolphin shows up with Parker the Platypus and asks a favor of Kowalski, he instantly jumps to her rescue only to find out its to free her brother Francis who happens to be a mind-jacked Dr. Blowhole.

title: The Penguins Of Madagascar: Marble Jar Head / Good Night And Good Chuck
description: How in the world is Rico supposed to behave well when King Julien has kidnapped his doll, Miss Perky?  When the Penguins try to get the anchor man Chuck Charles back on TV they find themselves in front of the camera.

title: Best and Bester: In the Sky / Best Buddies
description: Best and Bester are a pair of hilariously individual twins who live in a weird and wonderful alternate reality where your neighbour could be a pair of disgruntled trousers or your best friend a floating cloud of bottom burp.

title: Best and Bester: Donut Disturb / The Cursed Amulet
description: Best and Bester are a pair of hilariously individual twins who live in a weird and wonderful alternate reality where your neighbour could be a pair of disgruntled trousers or your best friend a floating cloud of bottom burp.

title: Bubble Guppies: Good Morning Mr. Grumpfish!

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Pineapple Fever
description: Squidward gets stuck indoors with SpongeBob and Patrick during a storm.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Mooncation / Mr. Krabs Takes A Vacation

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: The Cent of Money
description: Mr. Krabs uses Gary to find spare change.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Welcome to the Bikini Bottom Triangle
description: SpongeBob and all the Bikini Bottom citizens disappear to an underwater resort.

title: SpongeBob SquarePants: The Monster Who Came To Bikini Bottom
description: A monster terrorizes Bikini Bottom until Patrick befriends the huge creature.  SpongeBob and all the Bikini Bottom citizens disappear to an underwater resort.

title: El Daawa Ammah
description: Moataz, is a happy-go-lucky guy who leads a life around his friends. After his mother moves in, they argue, and his luck is put to the test. She puts a curse on him that sends misfortune his way. Will he be able to break the curse?

title: Sea W Noss W Khamseh
description: Abbas Chahine, has literally 1h:35m to get hold of a promised cash amount enabling him to immigrate with his fiancee Rima to Copenhagen.

title: Kalb Balady
description: Rocky acquires special powers as a result of drinking dogs milk when he was a baby and now Lieutenant Baleegh tries to exploit his abilities in order to catch the bad guys!

title: Gedo Nahnooh
description: When their grandfather dies, his grandchildren hope for a fortune in inheritance. Instead, they find a will instructing them to hunt for a buried treasure in a psychiatric hospital.

title: Halimo, Osttorat Al Shawatea
description: The story of Halemo who works as a savior on the shores of Alexandria, but still does not swim well and from here arise many comedy situations.

title: Caramel
description: The story revolves around five girls working in a womens beauty salon in Beirut, each of them has her own problem that she is trying to solve, can they do that?

title: Farha
description: During the 1948 Nakba, 14-year-old Farha’s dream of education shatters as she’s forced to hide in a storage room, witnessing her village’s violent destruction.

title: Between Heaven And Earth
description: Two married young couple are going through steps to get divorced when the husband finds out secrets about his past.

title: Youm W Leila
description: The story revolves around a policeman whos investigating some social issues, especially those related to the crises of the poor and the problems they face.

title: Bahebek
description: The events follow the life of a self-made businessman who finds himself caught between the woman hes about to marry and an old flame who comes back into his life.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Dr. No
description: Doctor No is in the house, ladies, and gentlemen, Faraj never spared anyone’s feelings in previous episodes with his unapologetic critique. Will he finally become the healer he is supposed to be, or will he get a taste of his own medicine in tonight’s episode?

title: Yalla Net`asha: DD FOXX
description: It is back to the Eighties in this episode as singer extraordinaire DD. Foxx welcomes her guests for some home cooking with a dress code inspired from the pop culture of the 80is. Question is, will she be crowned Top of the Pops or will she end up as one hit wonder?

title: Yalla Net`asha: Roa
description: Roa has the Hollywood Smile, but does she have golden fingers to win tonight? Our dentist extraordinaire is cooking Saudi cuisine with a dash of happiness and sweetness, lets hope someone has a sweet tooth, no pun intended.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Hair-raiser Ezzedine
description: with acting ambitions bigger than his hairdo, Ez leaves casting sessions for a chance at a leading role in tonights episode. So without further ado: Lights , Camera and Action.

title: Yalla Net`asha: Joumana strikes back
description: Tougher than diamonds or a diamond in the rough? Tonight, we find out what Joumana is really made of. Will she shine bright like a diamond or cut like a knife. Ouch!

title: Yalla Net`asha: The love birds
description: We welcome our first couples in the show. First on the starting line is the lovey-dovey Syrian couple Ziad and Sarra who want to show the world and their 6 guests that ‘all you need is love’, chopped onion and teamwork to win the 1000 dollars

title: Yalla Net`asha: Sidekicks
description: Second couple this week have the perfect shape and possibly the perfect recipe for culinary success. Will protein rich Egyptian cooking from the land of the pharaohs sooth the rising tensions of the previous night? Whatever the outcome, this night will be “Gheelicious”

title: Yalla Net`asha: Double Trouble
description: Levantine cuisine is under the spotlight tonight. Anne and Jean-Pierre have to live up to the expectations. With ample experience as food blogger, the task might seem easy for Anne but anyone will tell you, cooking with your partner is easier said than done .

title: Yalla Net`asha: On a knife-edge
description: This mother daughter team get on well together like house on fire. Will Kaother and Amani finally learn to be birds of a feather or will they mix like oil and water? Find out when we reveal the first winning couple in this exceptional season finale episode.
